title: KD Goes Down (Again), but the Warriors Survive | Heat Check
description:
Kevin Durant suffers an Achilles injury in his first game back, but the Golden State Warriors manage to pull out a win against the Toronto Raptors in Game 5 of the NBA Finals.

Host: John Gonzalez
Guest: Chris Ryan
